98792ff41cb40a471eef93b058","tid":1864222,"uid":74237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"朋友做護士<br />\n有醫生叫佢地罷工 有咩事佢同其他醫生會頂住<br />\n聽到都心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d207df261933f74bcbd6e75a395aad3e197b15e4","tid":1864222,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"有D真係走唔甩道德"},{"pid":"ad6b03ecf48a2d246b560c242b16191011c84850","tid":1864222,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339ff3aa1e988998792ff41cb40a471eef93b058","tid":1864222,"uid":74237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"朋友做護士<br />\n有醫生叫佢地罷工 有咩事佢同其他醫生會頂住<br />\n聽到都心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"為左唔出人命俾佢地安心罷工? 真心偉大<br />\n罷工最大既藍屍藉口就係「死人點算呀」"},{"pid":"77758f2520b7d021fb2f9fd24546129f337e411c","tid":1864222,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"醫生請病假要醫生紙，所以一定剩低一個請唔到假"},{"pid":"c71b45c50c69bcbd3ea490a978499927466ca876","tid":1864222,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:38:00.000Z","msg":"冇左份工你養"},{"pid":"ea860865517a8246425b7e57cc52ece77fa1e251","tid":1864222,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:38:28.000Z","msg":"要跟病人情況"},{"pid":"61072a14f18dc31a95ae477ea81a85412de062f7","tid":1864222,"uid":262901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:44:04.000Z","msg":"醫生真係成個春袋俾HA渣住，除非已經exit咗做specialist喺岀面就話大把世界，唔係嘅話做trainee佢唔俾你升或者唔俾你考試真係唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(不過呢個世界又真係有人成世都做緊lower trainee嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再唔係可以做gp... 哂就哂啲但係到最後都係自己取捨啫)"},{"pid":"e8ce7f6e3f49922121a29c75c8ccb5fae6054050","tid":1864222,"uid":11474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"其實醫生唔係你諗到咁冇得輸<br />\ntraining嗰啲都算 升唔到最後都10幾皮一個月<br />\n但真係比人炒<br />\n私家醫生市場未必食得哂所有人做gp<br />\n你話歐美缺醫護<br />\n姑娘去就易<br />\n醫生呢行外國保護主義勁過香港多多聲<br />\n要去外國practise其實直頭係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以先咁多人咁淆"},{"pid":"bfa61dfd8f0a8c431e29d4666e5bc54d854761bf","tid":1864222,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920a9918495afaeb6011dd68b84cafee83a4ebd2","tid":1864222,"uid":102993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:59:30.000Z","msg":"因為唔係每個人都有良心。唔止醫院嗰啲，有啲自人診所醫生都成日喺非應診期間用 Whatsapp ，向病人時常發表個人政見，例如: 黃基林醫生，會使用仇恨性言語罵人曱甴。<br />\n<br />\n資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edr.hk/doctor/info/wong-kee-lam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edr.hk%2Fdoctor%2Finfo%2Fwong-kee-lam&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=606e1803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edr.hk/doctor/info/wong-kee-lam</a>"}]}